вқҜ How can I run the test cuda_pin_test from another console?                    

в—Ҹ From another console, run:

  cd /home/dwaddington/certus/kernel/modules/nvidia_p2p/rust
  LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/home/dwaddington/.local/lib/python3.9/site-packages/nvidia/cu
  da_runtime/lib cargo test --test cuda_pin_test -- --nocapture

  Or export LD_LIBRARY_PATH first to keep the command shorter:

  export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/home/dwaddington/.local/lib/python3.9/site-packages/nv
  idia/cuda_runtime/lib
  cd /home/dwaddington/certus/kernel/modules/nvidia_p2p/rust
  cargo test --test cuda_pin_test -- --nocapture

